# Step 6: Configure NAT

## On Firewall VM

WAN Interface:

```text
ens160
```

Command:

```bash
iptables -t nat -A POSTROUTING \
-s 192.168.25.0/24 \
-o ens160 \
-j MASQUERADE
```

---

DMZ Internet Access:

```bash
iptables -t nat -A POSTROUTING \
-s 192.168.35.0/24 \
-o ens160 \
-j MASQUERADE
```

---

Verify:

```bash
iptables -t nat -L -n -v
```

